*[[卵圆阿布蛤|卵圆阿布蛤]] ''Abrina kinoshitai'' Kuroda et Habe, 1958
*[[小月阿布蛤|小月阿布蛤]] ''Abrina lunella'' Gould, 1861：又名[[月光唱片蛤|月光唱片蛤]]<ref name=TaiBNET_405268>{{TaiBNET |zh={{zh icon}} |id=405268 |binomial=Abrina lunella (Gould, 1861) |title=月光唱片蛤 }}</ref>
